thread.title_full: BRIEF-Spain to issue bonds due 2018, 2020 and 2025 on Thursday | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Spain to issue bonds due 2018, 2020 and 2025 on Thursday
text:
Sept 11 Spain's Treasury:
* Says it plans to issue bonds due 2018, 2020 and 2025 on Thursday
* Bonds include April 30, 2018, with a 0.25 percent coupon, July 30, 2020, with a 1.15 percent coupon and Oct. 31, 2025, with a 2.15 percent coupon
Source text for Eikon: (Reporting by Madrid Newsroom)
